props help to transfer data


Component A      props          Component B
data     >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>> data

Component A       Props                   Component B
(class)     >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>  data from class                       
data =>Api data
data will save in state
